sequenceDiagram
    participant Events as sec_events_stream<br/>(Memory Engine)
    participant Agent as AI SOC Agent
    participant Workspace as sec_case_workspace<br/>(Memory Engine)
    participant Graph as sec_users + sec_assets<br/>+ sec_access (SQL JOINs)
    participant ThreatDB as sec_threat_intel<br/>(MergeTree + Vector)
    participant History as sec_historical_incidents<br/>(MergeTree + Vector)

    Note over Events,History: Step 1 -- HOT MEMORY
    Agent->>Events: SELECT high-severity events<br/>with triage scoring
    Events-->>Agent: Top alert: login_success by user-006<br/>on asset-001 from 185.220.101.47

    Note over Events,History: Step 2 -- HOT MEMORY
    Agent->>Workspace: INSERT correlated events<br/>(same user, asset, IP -- last 60 min)
    Workspace-->>Agent: Case CASE-xxx created<br/>with N events correlated

    Note over Events,History: Step 3 -- GRAPH MEMORY
    Agent->>Graph: SELECT user profile, asset criticality,<br/>access rights (3 SQL JOINs)
    Graph-->>Agent: User: DB Admin, MFA: NO<br/>Asset: CRITICAL / PII, Has access: YES

    Note over Events,History: Step 4 -- WARM MEMORY
    Agent->>ThreatDB: Exact IoC lookup on IP<br/>+ cosineDistance vector search
    ThreatDB-->>Agent: MATCH: FIN6 / Operation FinFisher<br/>Confidence: 95%

    Note over Events,History: Step 5 -- WARM MEMORY
    Agent->>History: cosineDistance vector search<br/>for similar attack patterns
    History-->>Agent: Top match: Admin account<br/>compromised via credential stuffing

    Note over Events,History: Step 6 -- HOT MEMORY
    Agent->>Events: SELECT behaviour analytics<br/>for user-006 and src IP
    Events-->>Agent: Behaviour risk score: 0.70<br/>(HIGH RISK)

    Note over Events,History: Step 7 -- RESULT
    Agent->>Agent: Synthesise threat context<br/>Confidence: 80%<br/>Response: IMMEDIATE suspension
